ame arrived in Marseille in April and took two bronzes in the pool in Paris - but he wants to move on.\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9982573188257196, \"rank\": 0.001742650519158406, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1045, \"end\": 1054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.799200248054726e-12, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}, {\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0438474781748058e-27, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Manaudou\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"the first torchbearer\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic flame\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"two bronzes\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been very complicated emotionally since the end of the Games,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone keeps plunging me back in.\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not blame anyone, it's completely normal but I want to move forward.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want to be stuck in August 2024 for months and months.\\\"\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the capital, the dismantling of the temporary Olympic venues is almost complete.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"the dismantling\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"the temporary Olympic venues\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic rings have been taken down from the Eiffel Tower and the airborne cauldron in the Tuileries Gardens which proved such a hit has been taken down and is in search of a new home.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuileries_Palace\", \"score\": 0.9999988914320744, \"rank\": 1.108569207249185e-06, \"text\": \"Tuileries Gardens\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuileries_Palace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuileries_Palace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic rings\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"the airborne cauldron\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"such a hit\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1612}, {\"ngram\": \"search\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"a new home\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The grounds of the Palace of Versailles, which required major alterations to host the equestrian events, will not be completely restored until early 2025.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1752, \"end\": 1762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9996302554424975, \"rank\": 0.0003661612332206702, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The grounds\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"the Palace\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"Versailles\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"major alterations\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The lights have gone out at the local organising committee's main headquarters in Saint-Denis and the body has moved to smaller premises north of Paris.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1974, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1904, \"end\": 1915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 0.618658154400508, \"rank\": 0.6162616811855613, \"text\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0438474781748058e-27, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The lights\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"the local organising committee's main headquarters\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"smaller premises\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But its president Tony Estanguet, a three-time Olympic canoeing champion, remains hard at work, with estimations expected in December as to whether the budget exceeded \\u20ac4.5 billion (S$6.4 billion).\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1994, \"end\": 2008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its president\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"a three-time Olympic canoeing champion\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2070}, {\"ngram\": \"estimations\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2088}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"the budget\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2134}, {\"ngram\": \"S$6.4\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The government has not yet revealed the entire bill for the latest public costs, including bonuses granted to police officers.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The government\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire bill\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest public costs\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"bonuses\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"police officers\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Nov 7, France's general budget rapporteur, Charles de Courson, estimated that \\u20ac1.9 billion had not been budgeted for.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2313, \"end\": 2319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999999971792477, \"rank\": 2.6193529442188347e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2349, \"end\": 2367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Courson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charles de Courson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Courson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Courson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nov\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Minister Delegate for the Budget and Public Accounts, Laurent Saint-Martin, responded that the sum represented additional costs from using staff from the interior and defence ministries.\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2479, \"end\": 2499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Saint-Martin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurent Saint-Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Saint-Martin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Saint-Martin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Minister Delegate\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"the Budget\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2457}, {\"ngram\": \"Public Accounts\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2477}, {\"ngram\": \"the sum\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2523}, {\"ngram\": \"additional costs\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2552}, {\"ngram\": \"staff\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2569}, {\"ngram\": \"the interior and defence ministries\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone will say 'it cost more than expected but given the image we left, it is well worth this excess,\\\" one former elected official insisted.\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"the image\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2679}, {\"ngram\": \"one former elected official\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, increased consumption around the Olympics boosted French growth, with the economy expanding 0.4 per cent in the July-September quarter.\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2818, \"end\": 2824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9982573188257196, \"rank\": 0.001742650519158406, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2766}, {\"ngram\": \"increased consumption\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2809}, {\"ngram\": \"the economy\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2849}, {\"ngram\": \"0.4 per cent\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2872}, {\"ngram\": \"the July-September quarter\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the other hand, declining funding for sport for 2025, against a backdrop of a dip in public finances, has upset almost all stakeholders.\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 3044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other hand\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"declining funding\", \"from\": 2924, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2951}, {\"ngram\": \"a backdrop\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"a dip\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 2989}, {\"ngram\": \"public finances\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3008}, {\"ngram\": \"almost all stakeholders\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Barely a month after the closing ceremony of the Paralympic Games, what remains of the 'great sporting nation'?\\\"\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3088}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'great sporting nation\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ecology lawmaker Jean-Claude Raux asked.\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ecology lawmaker Jean-Claude Raux\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have the impression that nothing happened,\\\" Belkhir Belhaddad, co-president of the Olympic monitoring group in the French parliament, told AFP.\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3250, \"end\": 3267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belkhir_Belhaddad\", \"score\": 0.9999999989136086, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Belkhir Belhaddad\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belkhir_Belhaddad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belkhir_Belhaddad\"}, {\"begin\": 3321, \"end\": 3338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Parliament\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2326618637243023e-38, \"text\": \"French parliament\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Parliament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Parliament\"}, {\"begin\": 3345, \"end\": 3348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999907440724, \"rank\": 7.853205083416215e-09, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the impression\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3225}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"co\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3271}, {\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3281}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic monitoring group\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, sports clubs have seen their numbers rise, particularly in Paris, where table tennis, fencing and swimming - three sports in which France won Olympic medals - have all seen a marked increase in interest.\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3424, \"end\": 3429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank